{"tid":1695621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生證印防止自殺電話 學生打通卻是色情熱線","createTime":"2019-11-05T17:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T08:01:01.000Z","uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc1163bfbe923a206bc20d4275ce1dec94887c4","tid":1695621,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/11/04/99/7025891.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F11%2F04%2F99%2F7025891.jpg&h=14b6062f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n娜維爾撥打學生證後方的防止自殺熱線，不過接通之後卻發現號碼其實是一個色情電話。 圖／截取自KCBS影片<br />\n<br />\n電話打錯一個字，隨時接通一個令人尷尬的對話。近日美國有學生撥打學生證後方的防止自殺熱線，不過接通之後卻發現號碼其實是一個色情電話，引起不少人討論。校方其後表示學生證上的熱線電話出錯，將會盡快為所有學生更換學生證。<br />\n事發於美國加州蘭卡斯特（Lancaster）的中學New Vista Middle School，學生娜維爾（Emily Lavelle）與朋友在上周一（28日）放學後覺得無聊，於是決定打電話給印在學生證背後的24小時防止自殺熱線。不過電話接通後，她發現自己打了給一條色情電話熱線，傳來一把誘人的女聲及背景音樂，而非防止自殺熱線，「我覺得很震驚，因為這原本應該是幫助別人的熱線」。<br />\n<br />\n娜維爾當時想直接打電話給學校報告事件，可是由於當時學校的辦工時間已過，所以她就拍下學生證背後的電話並上載到facebook，照片很快就被瘋傳。可是她的帖文隔日（周三）就被fb刪除，指她的照片含有成人色情服務資訊，違反了社群使用守則。<br />\n<br />\n事後校方沒有直接回應娜維爾，而蘭卡斯特校區主管保華斯（Michelle Bowers）就發表道歉聲明，指他們於周一晚上發現中學學生證背後的防止自殺熱線出錯，對此感到很抱歉，將會盡力修正資料。校區解釋錯誤的原因是不小心將電話的兩個字掉轉，而印在學生證的上錯誤電話的確是色情電話熱線。現時校方已經將所有學生證收回，將盡快重印新證派發給學生。<br />\n<br />\n保華斯又提到，現時錯誤的號碼已經轉駁至正確的防止自殺熱線，「當色情熱線的擁有人知道這個問題之後，就十分友善地將所有撥入的電話都轉駁到防止自殺熱線」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6813/4144228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6813%2F4144228&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=d9fca012\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6813/4144228</a>"},{"pid":"c48529ef281e8dbbcf86e34ab187ccecc6f2f3c5","tid":1695621,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9776001ab2e2668705fa5f551dab0ed33bb45fa0","tid":1695621,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4ac14bac309e9c519f50d6779c64e0c521251e","tid":1695621,"uid":9125,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:42:14.000Z","msg":"某種意思上，都係防自殺電話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d9718e0ae06341fbe17b6ba85d50a17996c80c","tid":1695621,"uid":213607,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:44:04.000Z","msg":"病危打飛機重生果幅漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cabbe73986c589a05b7a1bba5c19b3cfb1fde7d","tid":1695621,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:45:41.000Z","msg":"性高潮時大腦會釋放腦內啡，讓人產生愉悅感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad2deaa80fe35b6d228d4203b8326324c4441c6","tid":1695621,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T18:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2108455121603b7cb32cf31e3bbb36e00f6b57","tid":1695621,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}